## 01 — Verified Remaining Gaps

### 🔴 P0 — Commercial Blockers (verified)

| Gap | Evidence | Scalability/Security note |
|-----|----------|--------------------------|
| **OTA Channel Manager is mock-only** | `channel-manager.ts` pushes to `webhookUrl` via axios — real OTA API auth (OAuth, XML, Channex) not wired | Multi-tenant: per-channel credentials must be stored encrypted in `ChannelConnection`, not env vars |
| **SMS is a console.log stub** | `sms.ts` line 12: `console.log('[SMS MOCK]')` — confirmed | Must use MSG91 Flow API with DLT-registered templates (TRAI mandate for India) |
| **8 `confirm()` dialogs remain** | Found in: `coupons/page.tsx:61`, `rooms/page.tsx:46,63,199,310,543`, `front-desk/page.tsx:78,71` | Replace with Sonner action toasts — confirm() is synchronous, blocks the JS thread |
| **No Schema.org `LodgingBusiness` JSON-LD** | Zero results for `jsonld`, `LodgingBusiness`, `application/ld+json` in entire `[slug]` directory | Critical for Google Hotel Ads free listing eligibility and organic SEO |
| **Razorpay wired for property payments; NOT for platform SaaS subscriptions** | `payments/router.ts` handles guest booking payments; admin `platform/router.ts` has no Razorpay for plan purchases | Platform subscription checkout (owner paying iStays) needs separate Razorpay flow |

### 🟡 P1 — Operational Gaps (verified)

| Gap | Evidence | Notes |
|-----|----------|-------|
| **POS module has zero frontend** | `packages/api/src/modules/pos/router.ts` = 385 lines; `apps/web/app/dashboard/` has no `pos/` directory | Backend is feature-complete; no dashboard UI at all |
| **Night audit has no dashboard UI** | `apps/web/app/dashboard/night-audit/` — directory exists; check if it has a working page | 54-line router exists; check UI completeness |
| **GST place-of-supply (intra vs inter-state)** | Schema has `placeOfSupply` field on `Invoice`; no code found that sets CGST+SGST vs IGST based on property state vs guest billing state | Legal compliance risk: wrong split = GST penalty |
| **GSTR-1 export** | No `gstr` or `gstr1` in codebase — only per-invoice GST fields | Monthly filing helper report needed for accountants |
| **Pre-arrival + post-checkout notification jobs** | No BullMQ job or `node-cron` scheduling confirmed for reminder sends | WhatsApp service exists; no scheduler wires it |
| **Promo/coupon backend validation in IBE** | `Coupon` model + migration `20260422184045_add_coupons` exists; `coupons/router.ts` exists; IBE booking widget may not call validate endpoint | Verify `22-property-public-page.spec.ts` or `24-promo-codes.spec.ts` covers the IBE path |
| **Rate season multipliers applied at booking time** | `RateSeason` model + `pricing.ts` service exist; needs code-level verification that `calculatePricing()` checks `RateSeason` date overlap | If not applied, seasonal pricing is DB-only, never billed |
| **Staff invite email flow** | `TenantMembership` model exists; need to verify `POST /tenants/:id/invite` endpoint and email send | Without it, owners can't add staff |

### 🟠 P2 — Security / Scalability / Standards (verified)

| Gap | Evidence | Impact |
|-----|----------|--------|
| **Rate limiter is in-memory (per-process)** | `rate-limit.ts` uses `Map<>` — confirmed; cleanup exists but per-process only | Behind N load-balanced replicas, effective limit = N × max. Must move to Redis sliding window for horizontal scale |
| **Socket.IO Redis adapter missing** | `socket.io` used but no `@socket.io/redis-adapter` found | Real-time room status won't sync across API pods |
| **node-cron runs per-process** | Night audit uses cron; no distributed lock | Duplicate night audit on multi-pod deploy — causes double room charges |
| **AES-256 encryption for ID document images** | `BookingGuest.idProofImageUrl` field exists; no encryption wrapper found in check-in-out router | PRD §3.14 legal requirement; DPDP Act 2023 compliance |
| **DPDP Act data export / erasure API** | No `dsar` or `data-export` endpoint found | Required before commercial launch; 72-hour delivery SLA |
| **Zod missing on 10+ API routes** | `gap-analysis.html` confirmed 9 modules WITH Zod, 10 WITHOUT | Mass-assignment risk on non-booking routes |
| **Audit log missing on 13 modules** | `gap-analysis.html` confirmed 12/25 have audit logging | Incomplete audit trail for compliance |
| **`N+1` in check-in room update** | Sequential `prisma.room.update()` per room — use `updateMany` | OK for <5 rooms; slow for group bookings |

